oman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">ACM ICMR</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">．</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">年，</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">Best Paper Award</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">PCM</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">．</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">年，</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">IEEE transactions on Multimedia</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">，最佳论文提名奖</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">．</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">2017</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">年，安徽省自然科学一等奖</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">．</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">2020</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">年，安徽省科技进步一等奖</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `wz_leader` VALUES (4, '何向南', '副院长', '/uploads/20221117/e96e2d85922fa608442bdc8bba47486f.jpg', '现任合肥综合性国家科学中心数据空间研究院副院长。教授、博士生导师，青年国家创新人才。致力于信息检索、数据挖掘、机器学习、因果推理等大数据与人工智能领域前沿研究，成果丰硕。在CCFA类会议和期刊发表论文100余篇，如会议SIGIR、WWW、KDD、ACMMultimedia等和期刊IEEETKDE、ACMTOIS等，谷歌...', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:黑体;color:#333333;background: white\"><img src=\"/uploads/20221117/e96e2d85922fa608442bdc8bba47486f.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" width=\"286\" height=\"331\" style=\"width: 286px; height: 331px;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">现任合肥综合性国家科学中心数据空间研究院副院长。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"background-color: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; text-indent: 2em;\">教授、博士生导师，青年国家创新人才。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">致力于信息检索、数据挖掘、机器学习、因果推理等大数据与人工智能领域前沿研究，成果丰硕。在</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">CCF A</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">类会议和期刊发表论文</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">100</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">余篇，如会议</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">SIGIR、WWW、KDD、ACM Multimedia</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">等和期刊</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">IEEE TKDE、ACM TOIS</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">等，谷歌学术引用</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">18000</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">余次，研究成果在多个商业公司的线上系统获得应用，取得积极效果。获得</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">2021</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">年</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">Elsevier</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">中国高被引学者，</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">2022</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">年</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">AI 2000</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">人工智能最具影响力学者</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: \">“</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">信息检索与推荐</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: \">”</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">领域排名第一。担任多个期刊的编委</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: \">/</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">副主编，如</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">IEEE Transactions on Knowledge and Data Engineering (TKDE)、ACM Transactions on Information Systems (TOIS), AI Open</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;\">等。主持多项国家级项目，如基金委面上项目、重点项目，科技部重点研发计划课题等。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">所获荣誉：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333\">1.<span style=\"font:9px \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">2020</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">月，获得</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">2020</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">年阿里巴巴达摩院青橙奖</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">（获奖理由：他聚焦个性化推荐，为信息过载精准施策。）</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roma