=\"font:9px \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">2018</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">年，</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">ACM Multimedia</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">最佳论文</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">Final List</span> </p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333\">6.<span style=\"font:9px \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">年，</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">SIGIR</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">最佳论文提名奖</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333\">7.<span style=\"font:9px \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">月，入选百度发布的全球首份</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',serif;color:#333333;background:white\">AI</span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background:white\">华人青年学者榜单。</span></p><p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);

