n></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(95, 156, 239); font-size: 19px; text-align: justify; visibility: visible;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 研究院介绍</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; opacity: 1; visibility: visible;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(95, 156, 239); font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; visibility: visible;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2022 RECRUIT /</p></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; visibility: visible;\"></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">数据空间研究院，隶属于四大综合性国家科学中心之一的合肥综合性国家科学中心，是十四五规划和2035年远景目标纲要的重要部署，是国家战略科技力量的重要组成部分。由安徽省人民政府直接发起设立，坐落于合肥市高新区，“科大硅谷”核心区。<br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">研究院由“国家最高科学技术奖”获得者王小谟院士出任首任院长，8位院士鼎力支持，汇聚全球顶尖科技人才。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(48, 55, 143); visibility: visible;\">以数据重构网络空间为核心理念，数据空间生态系统为核心体系，聚焦从数据到网络空间（From Data to Cyberspace）</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(48, 55, 143); visibility: visible;\">。</span></strong>在“人、机、物”三元融合的万物智能互联时代，通过数据空间感知、刻画、理解和分析预测，实现数据赋能、颠覆行业、定义未来。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">研究院拟筹建以数据创新平台(DataNet)为代表的重大科技基础设施，以国家重大战略任务为牵引，以优质人才团队培育为抓手，助力科技成果“落地生根”。目前已汇聚多支全球顶尖科技力量，包括感知与交互团队、知识产权大数据团队、隐私计算产品研发团队、心理大数据团队等，率先在政务、国防安全、卫生健康、智能汽车、教育等多领域开展产业化应用探索。已建成若干行业研究中心，包括焦聚数字经济发展的经济大数据研究中心；提升反垄断、反不当竞争效率的监管大数据研究中心；面向市域社会治理现代化和智慧城市需求的安全大数据研究中心；立足数字健康发展的健康大数据研究中心等。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(48, 55, 143);\">数据空间研究院诚邀海内外优秀科研人才加盟，申报“数创未来”全球引才计划。</span></strong>研究院拥有国家、安徽省、合肥市、高新区各层次人才奖励、培育、职称自主评定的政策优势，将全面支撑海内外优秀人才高质量的长期发展。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p></section><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: auto; min-width: 10%; height: auto; align-self: center;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !import